## 9. Tool Execution Lifecycle Summary

```
LLM decides to call a tool
  │
  ├─► tool_execution_start  (SDK event: toolCallId, toolName, args)
  │
  ├─► tool_call              (Extension event: CAN BLOCK, can mutate input)
  │     [if blocked → stop here]
  │
  ├─► execute() runs         (Custom tool impl)
  │     ├─► onUpdate()       (Streaming progress)
  │     ├─► throw            (Error → isError: true)
  │     └─► return value     (Success → isError: false)
  │
  ├─► tool_result            (Extension event: CAN MODIFY result, chain middleware)
  │
  ├─► tool_execution_end     (SDK event: result, isError)
  │
  └─► toolResult message event (Final message appended to conversation)
```

